notes.delta_definition: degradation_vs_clean is defined so delta>0 means worse under corruption for both higher- and lower-better metrics.
notes.gains_vs_sa_definition: robustness_gain_vs_SA = degradation_vs_clean(model) - degradation_vs_clean(SA); negative is better.
notes.missing_values: NaN/inf are omitted from metric dicts; missing keys imply null.
